is that we have computers

00:04:01.508 --> 00:04:06.180
that are about 50 or more times
faster than we did when we started.

00:04:06.246 --> 00:04:09.116
In fact, High Fidelity,
my new company,

00:04:09.716 --> 00:04:12.286
here, we are trying to build
virtual worlds

00:04:12.286 --> 00:04:16.089
that take advantage of all the speed
we have on modern PCs,

00:04:16.089 --> 00:04:17.959
and all the speed of the network,

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:20.729
as well as its latency,
its point-to-piont timing today.

00:04:20.729 --> 00:04:24.232
